{"tid":2443483,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"民主黨：超級區議會將會逐步孤立功能組別，時機一到功能組別將會廢除！","createTime":"2021-03-12T05:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T09:01:06.000Z","uid":219007,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4da394bfce952f069a683b3aacb53b897f89237","tid":2443483,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50QoR88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50QoR88.png&h=1afd73da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日我哋偉大嘅中央話改就改，唔知今日民主黨有咩感受呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7004e8550563502638743817538a2f6548452461","tid":2443483,"uid":114193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"做順民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為連下sir 忠實信徒<br />\n堅決支持連下sir 信念：<br />\n反黑暴，保政權，黃屍港毒一齊攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我copy連下sir 每日嘅大作你哋睇<br />\n震懾下你班連登黑暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大DQ學生會一事足以證明只能放棄香港，留底只能夠選擇表忠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2423210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2423210</a><br />\n<br />\n「安心出行」根本就冇得避，留底既香港人只會能夠接受～<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2401117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2401117</a><br />\n<br />\n依家講到明連選舉都唔俾你玩，請問啲留港抗爭撚點睇？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2417881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2417881</a><br />\n<br />\n［改變心態］香港變成點唔重要，最緊要自己活得開心就足夠！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2368342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2368342</a><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1</a><br />\n肥佬黎俾人告國安法，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1</a><br />\n中大畢業遊行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1</a><br />\n拜登贏咗，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1</a><br />\n就黎國安法實行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1</a><br />\n612一周年，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1</a><br />\n有武肺，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1</a><br />\nPoly 打完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1</a><br />\n要選區議會，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1</a><br />\n機場壓力測試完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1</a><br />\n8月大罷工完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1</a><br />\n728元朗遊行完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d2bde49d962edc2602e84461fa195e50af6f885a","tid":2443483,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T08:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ed1b8eb38f97ce430b96024f5d9a46317404db","tid":2443483,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:00:47.000Z","msg":"陳健民（2010）：隨着帶來超區五個議席後，相信小圈子選舉從此會成為歷史！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oV1b19O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoV1b19O.jpg&h=54b27df7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#歷史印記 #超級區議會 #Medium限定選圖<br />\n2010年超區政改方案通過後，民主黨和普選聯學者表示，新方案可以逐步令泛民主派議席數目增至接近2/3。 <br />\n<br />\n議事論事(2010年6月24日)：<br />\n//張文光(教育界，民主黨)：「直選會逐步包圍孤立功能組別，時機一到，揭竿起義，將功能組別廢除。」<br />\n<br />\n陳健民(中大社會學系副教授)：「這方案是左手叫停小圈子；右手為議會帶來5個直選議席。以後沒有互選或小圈子選舉，我相信從此成為歷史。所以憑良心講，怎可能不是將政制推前一步？關鍵在能否跟中央在一些基本政治問題上取得互信，特別是民主黨。」//"},{"pid":"bb73a383c7fba553398da15b2c85e57287e83dc6","tid":2443483,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:01:06.000Z","msg":"揭竿起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經犯左国安法，拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"56ed1b8eb38f97ce430b96024f5d9a46317404db","tid":2443483,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:00:47.000Z","msg":"陳健民（2010）：隨着帶來超區五個議席後，相信小圈子選舉從此會成為歷史！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oV1b19O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoV1b19O.jpg&h=54b27df7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#歷史印記 #超級區議會 #Medium限定選圖<br />\n2010年超區政改方案通過後，民主黨和普選聯學者表示，新方案可以逐步令泛民主派議席數目增至接近2/3。 <br />\n<br />\n議事論事(2010年6月24日)：<br />\n//張文光(教育界，民主黨)：「直選會逐步包圍孤立功能組別，時機一到，揭竿起義，將功能組別廢除。」<br />\n<br />\n陳健民(中大社會學系副教授)：「這方案是左手叫停小圈子；右手為議會帶來5個直選議席。以後沒有互選或小圈子選舉，我相信從此成為歷史。所以憑良心講，怎可能不是將政制推前一步？關鍵在能否跟中央在一些基本政治問題上取得互信，特別是民主黨。」//"}}